12805025.pdf#navpanes=1&view=FitH|title=\u00cdslenski Listinn Topp 40 (NR. 329 Vikuna 24.6. - 1.7. 1999)|publisher=Dagbla\u00f0i\u00f0 V\u00edsir|accessdate=July 14, 2018|language=is}}</ref>\n|6\t\n|-\n{{singlechart|Ireland2|1|song=Livin' la Vida Loca|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 9, 2016}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Italy (''[[Musica e dischi]]''/[[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]])<ref name=\"eu\"/>\n|4\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Japan ([[Oricon Singles Chart]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/artist/178059/ranking/cd_single/ |script-title=ja:\u30ea\u30c3\u30ad\u30fc\u30fb\u30de\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\u30f3\u306e\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u58f2\u308a\u4e0a\u3052\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 |language=Japanese |publisher=[[Oricon]] |accessdate=February 9, 2016 |url-status=unfit |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025035630/http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/artist/178059/ranking/cd_single/ |archivedate=October 25, 2014 }}</ref>\n|56\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch40|9|year=1999|week=24|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 9, 2016}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch100|11|artist=Ricky Martin|song=Livin' la Vida Loca|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 9, 2016}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|New Zealand|1|artist=Ricky Martin|song=Livin' la Vida Loca|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 9, 2016}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Norway|2|artist=Ricky Martin|song=Livin' la Vida Loca|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 9, 2016}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Romania ([[Romanian Top 100]])<ref name=\"rt100\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rt100.ro/topul-anului-1999.html|title=Romanian Top 100: Top of the Year 1999|language=Romanian|publisher=[[Romanian Top 100]]|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050122081829/http://www.rt100.ro/topul-anului-1999.html|archivedate=January 22, 2005|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|1\n|-\n{{singlechart|Scotland|2|date=1999-07-11|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 9, 2016}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Spain|2|artist=Ricky Martin|song=Livin' la Vida Loca|rowheader=true|accessdate=Febru